<template>

</template>

<script>
import axios from 'axios';
export default {
	data () {
		return {
			username:'',
			password:'',
			data_res:[],
			is_show:false,
			title:'',
			content:''
		}
	},
	methods: {

		//添加个人博客数据
		getaxios4(){
			if(this.username&&this.password){
				axios.post('/api//api/admin/addArticle/',{
					username:this.username,
					title:this.title,
					content:this.content
				}).then(res => {
					// this.data_res = res;
					console.log(res);
					}, res => {
						console.info('请求失败');
				})
			}else{
				alert('账号密码不能为空')
			}
		},

	},
};

</script>
